OL,3,C'Dangerous' to suggest corridor care
OL,4,Ccan be delivered safely ` emergency
OL,5,Cdoctors
OL,7,FLeading emergency doctors have
OL,8,Fexpressed concern about a new guide on
OL,9,Fhow to treat patients in corridors,
OL,10,Fsaying it is "normalising the
OL,11,Fdangerous".
OL,13,FNHS England has produced guidance on
OL,14,F"providing safe and good quality care
OL,15,Fin temporary escalation spaces".
OL,17,FBut the Royal College of Emergency
OL,18,FMedicine (RCEM) said the "nonsensical"
OL,19,Fguidance is "out of touch".
