OL,7,FResponding, RCEM said it is "not
OL,8,Fpossible to provide safe and good
OL,9,Fquality care" in corridors or
OL,10,Fcupboards.
OL,12,FIn a position statement released to
OL,13,Fthe PA news agency, the College said:
OL,14,F"Advice from arm's length bodies that
OL,15,Fappear out of touch with what is
OL,16,Fhappening in our departments was
OL,17,Falways going to be poorly received."
OL,26,@oD@]OUqD@MO]vD@AOUyD@dO]
