OL,7,FUse of corridors will lead to long
OL,8,Fwaits in emergency departments which
OL,9,Fis "associated with measurable harm to
OL,10,Fpatients", it added.
OL,12,FThe RCEM said patient privacy and
OL,13,Fdignity are "not maintained" when they
OL,14,Fare being cared for in corridors.
OL,16,FRest and sleep for patients is
OL,17,F"difficult, if not impossible" and
OL,18,Fpatient confidentiality "cannot be
OL,19,Fmaintained".
