OL,7,FMeanwhile, controlling the spread of
OL,8,Finfection "is not possible" and it is
OL,9,F"challenging" for staff to monitor
OL,10,Fpatients.
OL,12,FGiving patients the treatment they
OL,13,Fneed is "made more difficult and often
OL,14,Fdelayed", the College added.
OL,16,F"It is distressing for patients,
OL,17,Fparticularly the old and the
OL,18,Fvulnerable, to be in open, noisy,
OL,19,Fbrightly lit, often cold areas," the
OL,20,FRCEM position statement adds.
