OL,7,FThese points are "not consistent with
OL,8,Fgood quality care" and "render many of
OL,9,Fthe statements within the document
OL,10,Fnonsensical", the College added.
OL,12,FCollege president Dr Adrian Boyle, who
OL,13,Fpenned the position statement along
OL,14,Fwith vice-president Dr Ian Higginson,
OL,15,Fsaid: "While we understand why this
OL,16,Fguidance has been issued, as a College
OL,17,Fwe are concerned that it represents a
OL,18,Fnormalisation of what is an
OL,19,Funacceptable and dangerous situation.
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@RO]pD@XOUrD@LO]wD@GOU
