OL,5,Cdoctors
OL,7,F"It is not possible to provide truly
OL,8,Fsafe care in environments such as
OL,9,Fcorridors and cupboards.
OL,11,F"It also evidenced a lack of
OL,12,Funderstanding for what has been
OL,13,Fhappening in emergency departments for
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,F"So-called 'corridor care' is a result
OL,17,Fof overcrowding, which leads to
OL,18,Fextended A&E stays that we know
OL,19,Fcontribute to avoidable death.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
