OL,7,F"We and our members cannot, and will
OL,8,Fnot, accept this situation.
OL,10,F"Rather than advising how to deal with
OL,11,Fovercrowding, all effort should be
OL,12,Ffocused on preventing it."
OL,14,FProfessor Nicola Ranger, chief
OL,15,Fexecutive and general secretary at the
OL,16,FRoyal College of Nursing, said: "Care
OL,17,Fdelivered in corridors and other non-
OL,18,Fclinical spaces is unsafe, undignified
OL,19,Fand unacceptable.
