OL,7,FSenior midwife Donna Ockenden, who has
OL,8,Fled reviews into patient safety in the
OL,9,FNHS, said recently she felt corridor
OL,10,Fcare had become "normalised" after
OL,11,Fseeing laminated signs on walls
OL,12,Fsignposting where patients wait on
OL,13,Ftrolleys.
OL,15,FIn an interview with PA in October
OL,16,Fspeaking about her daughter's
OL,17,Femergency treatment at an unnamed
OL,18,Fhospital, she said: "Trolley waits,
OL,19,Fcorridor care, has become normalised.
