OL,7,F"There are even signs on the wall now
OL,8,Fwith numbers showing how many trolleys
OL,9,Fthey can have any one time.
OL,11,F"There's one particular corridor in
OL,12,Fthis A&E where there's space for five
OL,13,Ftrolleys, and literally the walls are
OL,14,Fnumbered with laminated signs."
OL,16,FThe news comes as some health
OL,17,Fcommentators warned hospitals are
OL,18,Frunning "red hot", with some
OL,19,Fpredicting winter could be "one of the
