OL,7,FThe latest figures show an average of
OL,8,F96,661 beds were filled each day last
OL,9,Fweek, 94.6% of the total available.
OL,11,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,12,Frecently ordered health service
OL,13,Fleaders to "prioritise patient safety"
OL,14,Fas winter approaches.
OL,16,FAmanda Pritchard, chief executive of
OL,17,Fthe NHS in England, has said "patient
OL,18,Fsafety must be paramount".
