OL,7,FAn NHS England spokesperson said: "As
OL,8,Fthe document ` developed with nurses
OL,9,Fand clinical leaders ` makes clear,
OL,10,FNHS England believes that caring for
OL,11,Fpatients in temporary spaces is not
OL,12,Facceptable, should never be considered
OL,13,Fas standard, and should only ever be
OL,14,Fused when all other options have been
OL,15,Fexhausted.
