OL,7,F"Patient flow through hospitals and
OL,8,Fcapacity in A&E has been impacted by
OL,9,Frecord levels of demand going into
OL,10,Fwinter, a jump in patients
OL,11,Fhospitalised with viruses like flu and
OL,12,Fnorovirus, and thousands of beds taken
OL,13,Fup by patients ready for discharge.
OL,15,F"NHS staff are working hard to provide
OL,16,Fthe safest possible care for patients
OL,17,Fthis winter, including better use of
OL,18,Flive data, an expansion of same day
OL,19,Femergency care, and more care in the
OL,20,Fcommunity."
